column5: Hey gang!!! I'm looking for a few helpers. See attached ad.
Dang!  That last specification cuts me out!  I was already practicing left handed death laser until I saw that!  Michael
This stuff is great Dave but fudge, you're up in God's country, where's all the fish reports?

Been too busy with the cabin. I only got out fishing twice this winter. Now I have to fix my sled and get my boat ready while waiting for ice out. The sled has to be done now as I don't want to have to fix it up while waiting for ice up in late October. The weather outside is much nicer now.  I'll be getting the boat out as soon as there is some open water to fish though.
I'll be getting the boat out as soon as there is some open water to fish though. That's generally Labour Day weekend up there  isn't it
I think I've worked for him before.
I'll buy the evil part but the second word in the leaders title I wonder about
